description: Try our easy to follow Chocolate Raspberry Ice Cream Cake recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Chocolate Raspberry Ice Cream Cake Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Turn ice cream out onto a serving plate. Decorate with chocolate curls and top with extra raspberries if desired. Serve immediately.
